{"word":"G1843 - ἐξομολογέω - exomologéō - ex-om-ol-og-eh'-o - Confess","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐξομολογέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">exomologéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ex-om-ol-og-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Confess</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஸ்தோத்திரி, அறிக்கையிடு, சம்மதி"},{"paragraph":"1. to confess"},{"paragraph":"2. to profess, to acknowledge openly and joyfully"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G3670 - ὁμολογέω - homologéō - hom-ol-og-eh'-o/3670\">G3670</a>; to <i>acknowledge</i> or (by implication of <i>assent</i>) <i>agree fully:</i> - confess, profess, promise.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1843/1843\">G1843</a>, <a href=\"#/G3670/3670\">G3670</a>, <a href=\"#/G3671/3671\">G3671</a>, <a href=\"#/G3672/3672\">G3672</a>, <a href=\"#/G437/437\">G437</a>"}]}